com.cerner.bunsen.r4.codes

Class ValueSets

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.codes.base.AbstractValueSets<ValueSet,ValueSets>
      • com.cerner.bunsen.r4.codes.ValueSets

  • public class ValueSets
extends AbstractValueSets<ValueSet,ValueSets>
    An immutable collection of FHIR ValueSets. This class is used to import value set content, explore it, and persist it to a database.
